 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/court-to-rule-on-police-officer-accused-of-killing-ethiopian-israeli-in-2019/0000018e-9d52-dc54-a19f-9f7e39420000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡前总理办公室主任就腐败案作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/ex-pmo-chief-testifies-in-netanyahu-corruption-case/0000018e-9d52-d764-adff-9fdf0fe70000</link><description>2009-2011 年担任总理办公室主任的埃亚尔·加拜 (Eyal Gabai) 表示，“我个人不准备做违背我对国家利益的信念的事情”，该案涉及内塔尼亚胡被指控的第 1000 号案件欺诈和违反信任</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 08:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/ex-pmo-chief-testifies-in-netanyahu-corruption-case/0000018e-9d52-d764-adff-9fdf0fe70000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德称，在开罗起草的新停火、释放人质提案已提交给哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article-live/alleged-israeli-strike-kills-several-world-central-kitchen-aid-workers-in-gaza/0000018e-9c9b-dfd2-afce-dcffeac70000</link><description>以色列国防军承诺对“悲惨”援助人员死亡事件进行独立彻底调查 ■ 伊朗最高领导人誓言对以色列大马士革罢工进行报复 ■ 世卫组织称希法医院“以任何形式”无法运作 ■ 前总统里夫林：以色列距此仅一步之遥免受国际排斥</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 02:33:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article-live/alleged-israeli-strike-kills-several-world-central-kitchen-aid-workers-in-gaza/0000018e-9c9b-dfd2-afce-dcffeac70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭导致加沙七名世界中央厨房援助人员丧生；以色列国防军：“悲剧事件”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-looking-into-hamas-claim-that-israeli-strike-killed-world-central-kitchen-aid-workers/0000018e-9c11-d64e-afce-ffb5c08d0000</link><description>三名死者身份已得到确认，其中包括两名外国援助人员及其巴勒斯坦司机； WCK：“人道主义援助人员和平民永远不应该成为目标。”以色列国防军：进行审查“以了解这一悲惨事件的情况”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 23:56:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-looking-into-hamas-claim-that-israeli-strike-killed-world-central-kitchen-aid-workers/0000018e-9c11-d64e-afce-ffb5c08d0000</guid></item><item><title>由于外国航空公司犹豫不决，往返以色列的航班成本下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/cost-of-flights-to-and-from-israel-dropping-as-foreign-airlines-make-hesitant-return/0000018e-9ad1-dfd2-afce-def5d35c0000</link><description>在经历了因战争而经历的高价冬季之后，随着外国航空公司的回归以及本古里安国际机场廉价航站楼于 6 月重新开放，机票价格开始下降</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 22:57:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/cost-of-flights-to-and-from-israel-dropping-as-foreign-airlines-make-hesitant-return/0000018e-9ad1-dfd2-afce-def5d35c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员对与哈马斯达成释放人质协议的前景持悲观态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-downbeat-on-prospects-for-hostage-release-deal-with-hamas/0000018e-9b55-dd2b-ad9f-db5f6ae00000</link><description>参加会谈的以色列代表团成员将留在开罗，但摩萨德主席戴维·巴尼亚不会加入他们的行列</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 22:23:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-downbeat-on-prospects-for-hostage-release-deal-with-hamas/0000018e-9b55-dd2b-ad9f-db5f6ae00000</guid></item><item><title>报道：内塔尼亚胡的妻子将获得以色列纳税人资助的“私人美发沙龙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/netanyahus-wife-to-get-private-hair-salon-funded-by-israeli-taxpayers/0000018e-9ba2-dd2b-ad9f-dbfa64500000</link><description>以以色列非官方第一夫人的“安全问题和高层威胁”为由，政府在总理耶路撒冷官邸附近租了一套空置公寓</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 22:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/netanyahus-wife-to-get-private-hair-salon-funded-by-israeli-taxpayers/0000018e-9ba2-dd2b-ad9f-dbfa64500000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗高级将军被暗杀加剧了以色列与伊朗和真主党的冲突，加剧了北部边境的紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/iranian-generals-assassination-signals-a-dangerous-turn-in-israels-northern-front/0000018e-9b3f-d64e-afce-ffbf18780000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列和真主党一直小心翼翼地避免全面战争，但大马士革造成叙利亚和黎巴嫩圣城军指挥官死亡的空袭表明，以色列不断提高向北方对手索取的价格</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/iranian-generals-assassination-signals-a-dangerous-turn-in-israels-northern-front/0000018e-9b3f-d64e-afce-ffbf18780000</guid></item><item><title>“人们不断咒骂辛瓦尔”：反对哈马斯的加沙人确信他们是大多数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/people-are-cursing-sinwar-gazans-opposing-hamas-are-sure-theyre-the-majority/0000018e-9ada-dfd2-afce-deff025f0000</link><description>接受《国土报》采访的四名加沙人对加沙地带的哈马斯领导人以及 10 月 7 日发动战争的决定表示不满。他们说，许多人担心哈马斯会因为他们的言论而惩罚他们，并指责阿拉伯媒体在报道时视而不见。有人批评该团体</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/people-are-cursing-sinwar-gazans-opposing-hamas-are-sure-theyre-the-majority/0000018e-9ada-dfd2-afce-deff025f0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在全麻下成功接受疝气手术</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-undergoes-successful-hernia-operation-under-full-anesthesia/0000018e-9ad1-d64e-afce-fff5513b0000</link><description>据他的办公室称，内塔尼亚胡完全清醒，状况良好，并被转移到康复病房</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 19:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-undergoes-successful-hernia-operation-under-full-anesthesia/0000018e-9ad1-d64e-afce-fff5513b0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗誓言对以色列高级将领在大马士革被杀一事作出“严厉”反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/iran/2024-04-01/ty-article/iran-blames-israel-for-syria-strike-threatens-harsh-response-for-killing-of-top-general/0000018e-9a50-d64e-afce-fff552490000</link><description>伊朗革命卫队表示，有七名革命卫队成员在袭击中丧生，而以色列拒绝就这一事件发表评论。这次袭击杀死