ue">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.highlight/ultra-orthodox-jews-wont-be-press-ganged-into-the-idf-overnight-but-change-is-coming/0000018e-99fe-dcec-a3ef-dbffd16e0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其反对派给独裁者埃尔多安以沉重打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/turkeys-opposition-lands-authoritarian-erdogan-a-shocking-blow/0000018e-9a35-dd2b-ad9f-da7f48730000</link><description>周日晚上，土耳其书写了历史：反对派在地方选举中取得如此巨大的胜利，标志着埃尔多安下台的第一天，以及重建正常运转的民主的机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/turkeys-opposition-lands-authoritarian-erdogan-a-shocking-blow/0000018e-9a35-dd2b-ad9f-da7f48730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列依靠武力，自取自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-israel-relies-on-force-it-sets-itself-up-for-suicide/0000018e-99e1-dd2b-ad9f-d9fb98760000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:43:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/as-israel-relies-on-force-it-sets-itself-up-for-suicide/0000018e-99e1-dd2b-ad9f-d9fb98760000</guid></item><item><title>“哈马斯喉舌”：内塔尼亚胡称赞允许他关闭以色列半岛电视台的新法律</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/netanyahu-pushes-ahead-law-for-immediate-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018e-99f0-de2c-afff-bbf8be670000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡宣布打算立即停止以色列“恐怖分子渠道”的活动，并声称该渠道参与了 10 月 7 日的大屠杀。白宫表示该法律“令人担忧”，并强调新闻自由的重要性</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 15:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/netanyahu-pushes-ahead-law-for-immediate-shutdown-of-al-jazeera-in-israel/0000018e-99f0-de2c-afff-bbf8be670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方表示，对加沙的希法医院进行突袭可能会获得有关以色列人质的重要情报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-01/ty-article/.pre